{"tid":1065342,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我認為警察應用警棍制服疑犯而非開槍","createTime":"2019-03-17T07:34:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-17T07:38:45.000Z","uid":28450,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"706a3146a700c39b50511ac9ed36e019993b8f1c","tid":1065342,"uid":28450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T07:34:00.000Z","msg":"首先，開槍有機會射不中疑犯而導致流彈，令其他人受傷。<br />\n其次，警棍是手臂的延伸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，使用上來更加靈活，而且警棍可攻可守，攻者可以攻擊疑犯的手臂乃至其他部位，令疑犯無力作惡<br />\n<br />\n守者可以用作格擋之用，每當疑犯劈向你，你可以猜測佢到底係由上而下劈，抑或由左右劈過來<br />\n一旦成功格擋，則可以換取一回合攻擊機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請問其他同學有何睇法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4934515b0df468997d6fda506bb7f41dcfd91220","tid":1065342,"uid":196735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T07:35:21.000Z","msg":"其實可以空手奪白刃，不過學堂無教"},{"pid":"625ea2cfc0034d8ae36a7b4ee1022271ff2a517f","tid":1065342,"uid":199613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T07:36:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />應該用念力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f64f5ff1a6d9d379f0684fe00ad7eea191fcc3e8","tid":1065342,"uid":28450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4934515b0df468997d6fda506bb7f41dcfd91220","tid":1065342,"uid":196735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T07:35:21.000Z","msg":"其實可以空手奪白刃，不過學堂無教"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T07:36:32.000Z","msg":"太危險了<br />\n至少要有警棍 防守<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c22fce7c567cec7c47a53c87c87fcc0154c4b7d","tid":1065342,"uid":14065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T07:36:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.y